
First install Microsoft Visual C++ redistributable 2015 by the following link Download Visual C++ Redistributable for Visual Studio 2015 from Official Microsoft Download Center 47

Install anaconda3 for windows from its sites.

Then create a virtual python environment and activate the created virtual environment. 

#conda create -n rasa python=3.6
#conda activate rasa

Now install rasa  by following Rasa docs for installation in that created python environment. # pip install rasa

During installation httptools package not found error will come. Then install by following command #conda install -c conda-forge httptools




conda install -c anaconda ujson